- Contributed to the cloud based automated healthcare claims platform eClaim.
- Built user, admin, and manager auth with React for seamless login and access control.
- Developed dynamic UI, breadcrumbs, and multi page navigation that improved workflow efficiency by 25 percent.
- Integrated REST APIs across frontend and backend.
- Assisted backend schema design and query optimization on PostgreSQL.
- Led testing and debugging, reducing defect rates by 20 percent after launch.
